title: Felici Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Italian, Juice bar, Take-out, Caribbean, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Several salads contain nuts, edamame, chickpeas, and tofu; has a marinated vegetable sandwich.  Dressings are labeled vegan. Also smoothie, coffee, and juice bar. Fun atmosphere with bright colors, Wi-Fi. Staff is knowledgeable about what vegan means.
